(23, 3, 12, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">COVID-19</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">As of <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Oct 2024</strong>, the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">COVID-19 vaccine mandate</strong> for healthcare workers in <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Victoria (VIC)</strong> has been <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">revoked</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Despite this, individual healthcare facilities may still choose to implement their own policies regarding COVID-19 vaccination depending on their risk assessments and workplace safety regulationsâ€‹</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\" target=\"_blank\">TGA Gov Au International COVID-19 vaccines recognised by Australia</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break;\"><!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">COVID-19 Primary dose 1&amp;2 and COVID-19 dose 3/Booster </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a temporary or permanent medical exemption.</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:09:16', '2025-03-12 12:41:19'),
(24, 3, 13, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Diphtheria, Tetanus, Pertussis (dTpa)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Since healthcare workers are required to have protection against all three&mdash;diphtheria, tetanus, and pertussis (dTpa)&mdash;the ADT vaccine alone is not sufficient or acceptable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Pertussis serology: Serological testing is not considered a reliable or valid method for determining immunity to pertussis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required:&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a single dose of dTpa vaccine within the last 10 years.</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:09:16', '2025-01-10 05:11:36'),
(25, 3, 14, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis A</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/contents/vaccine-preventable-diseases/hepatitis-a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Health Gov Au Hepatitis A immunisation handbook </a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 5.0pt 0in 5.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Victoria</strong> the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Hepatitis A vaccine</strong> is <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">not mandatory</strong> for all healthcare workers, but it is required for specific high-risk roles. These roles include healthcare workers who are working in remote Indigenous communities, with Indigenous children, or in areas where sanitation is a concern.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 5.0pt 0in 5.0pt 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">If you are working in these high-risk settings, it is recommended or required to receive the H